survey_response.review_text: I am 29 year old person. I was having severe pain in my tooth. My friend recommended me to visit Vibgyor Dental Clinic. Before visiting the clinic I had word with Dr. Bhavesh Rusawat on phone. He was very cordial in his approach. When I visited the clinic I was awestruck by the look of it. The clinic was state-of-the-art and had vibrant colored rooms. It has separate rooms for different functionalities. In short it had all the facilities in one clinic. I need not wait at the reception and was taken into treatment at the same time as I had appointment. The treatment was painless. I had filling done in my teeth. Now after few days I can eat anything hot and cold without any pain in my tooth. I would surely recommend Vibgyor dental clinic to my family members,peers and friends.

I was relex that I was in safe hands... After 15 days my all pain n problems were solved.. I m strongly recommend this Dr.Bhavesh... he is very nice in his profession...friendly .. very explanarltive... N god harted....thank u Dr.😊😊😊😊
